snippet.title: Super Metroid World - Minigame - NCFC 2009
snippet.description: DeProgrammer's "Super Metroid World" (Nintendo DS homebrew) made for the 2009 Nintendo Community Fangame Convention minigame contest. Download it at http://www.filefront.com/14840391/SuperMetroidWorld.zip . DeProgrammer recommends using the no$gba emulator to play it.
